00:05:39,670 --> 00:05:41,240
of light as being very large,

149
00:05:41,500 --> 00:05:44,900
and this piece here is essentially negligible.

150
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:48,620
And d tau is the same as dt.

151
00:05:49,300 --> 00:05:51,620
So for slowly moving objects

152
00:05:51,620 --> 00:05:56,040
in a frame of reference which,

153
00:05:56,040 --> 00:05:56,440
uh,

154
00:05:56,760 --> 00:05:58,260
