158
00:06:08,220 --> 00:06:09,500
But more generally,

159
00:06:09,560 --> 00:06:12,760
if we're interested in things which are moving fast,

160
00:06:13,540 --> 00:06:16,920
then this is the proper time along a trajectory.

161
00:06:17,220 --> 00:06:20,200
It's the time as recorded by a clock

162
00:06:20,200 --> 00:06:22,020
